Project Overview

Collection Grid Section is a modern and reusable custom Shopify section built to showcase collections in a clean grid-based layout. This component helps merchants present multiple product categories in an organized and visually engaging format while maintaining full customization through the theme editor.

The section supports dynamic images, titles, links, and responsive layouts for all device sizes.

Features

✅ Responsive 4-column grid layout
✅ Dynamic collection blocks
✅ Merchant-editable content
✅ Hover zoom image effect
✅ Lazy-loaded images
✅ Mobile-first responsive design
✅ Clean UI and optimized spacing
✅ Easy scalability for multiple collections

